item.title: CVE-2024-29219|2024-04-15T10:41:33.292Z -- keyence%20corporation -- kv%20studio
item.description: Out-of-bounds read vulnerability exists in KV STUDIO Ver.11.64 and earlier and KV REPLAY VIEWER Ver.2.64 and earlier, which may lead to information disclosure or arbitrary code execution by having a user of the affected product open a specially crafted file.
